msgctxt "112_Elise Manager"
msgid "Hello, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Hola, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "124_Akiyama"
msgid "Yo. I thought I'd drop in and check on the club. How are\\r\n"
"things?"
msgstr "Hey. Pase a ver como estaban las cosas en el club. ¿Va todo\\r\n"
"bien?"

msgctxt "136_Elise Manager"
msgid "Remarkably well, given the state of the economy."
msgstr "Considerando esta economía, increíblemente bien."

msgctxt "148_Akiyama"
msgid "Really? That's good to hear."
msgstr "¿Ah, de verdad? Es bueno oírlo."

msgctxt "160_Elise Manager"
msgid "But..."
msgstr "Pero..."

msgctxt "172_Akiyama"
msgid "But what?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "184_Elise Manager"
msgid "Well, it's Miki..."
msgstr "Se trata de Miki..."

msgctxt "196_Akiyama"
msgid "What about her?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con ella?"

msgctxt "208_Elise Manager"
msgid "Maybe you'd better ask her yourself. She's in today."
msgstr "Ella está aquí hoy. Será mejor que le preguntes tú mismo."

msgctxt "220_Akiyama"
msgid "All right. Have her stop by the dressing room."
msgstr "Entiendo. Pídele que vaya al camerino."

